body_html:
We need to fix the ongoing Python 3.5 build failure in nightly before the Jenkins configuration can be updated for nightly-docker-cpu and nightly-docker-gpu and this can be merged.
For example, see http://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-python35-linux-cpu/
